dialogue.introduction: Nice to meet you, I'm Tatsuta~. I hope Tenryuu-chan hasn't been causing you trouble?
dialogue.library_intro: Light cruiser Tatsuta, second of Tenryuu class. I come from Sasebo. I hope Tenryuu-chan hasn't been causing everybody trouble? You really can't take your eyes off that girl, right? Huh? Me? Well, I'm not particularly fond of submarines~
dialogue.secretary1: Waah, it's dangerous if you suddenly talk from behind me, you know.
dialogue.secretary2: Is there something on your mind?
dialogue.secretary3: Touching is forbidden~ That hand, don't blame me if it falls off.
dialogue.secretaryidle: I'm a little bored~. Well, it's okay because I'll do what I want to~
dialogue.wedding: Having favour from the Admiral is nice. B~ut, if I'm all friendly with the Admiral, Tenryuu-chan will be all alone, you know~. I'm sorry, okay~?
dialogue.show_players_score: A message for you~. It'd be nice if every message brought good news~.
dialogue.joining_a_fleet: Time for a sortie. Now where's a ship who wants to die?
dialogue.equipment1: Oh~ It seems I've become stronger again.
dialogue.equipment2: Thank you. Don't tell Tenryuu-chan about it. That girl gets sulky easily.
dialogue.docking_minor_damage: I want to relax like this for a while~
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: A~Ah, I'm all tattered~ I'll sleep in the dock for a while, futons are happiness~
dialogue.docking_complete: It looks like somebody's done repairing~
dialogue.ship_construction: Looks like a newcomer has arrived~
dialogue.return_from_sortie: The fleet has returned? Looks like the operation has ended~
dialogue.start_a_sortie: Where is the enemy? My torpedoes are anxious.
dialogue.attack: Oh~ have you lost your voice?
dialogue.night_battle: Let's give chase~ They absolutely will not escape.
dialogue.night_attack: Aren't I more skilled than Tenryuu-chan~?
dialogue.artillery_spotting: Aren't I more skilled than Tenryuu-chan~?
dialogue.night_special_attack_modifier_cutin_at_n: Aren't I more skilled than Tenryuu-chan~?
dialogue.support_expedition_team_arrival: Aren't I more skilled than Tenryuu-chan~?
dialogue.mvp: Eh, me? I've still got more to go~ Hey, Tenryuu-chan's got such an ama~zing glaring face, ufufu~
dialogue.minor_damaged2: Noo, my clothes~ ...I won't forgive you...
dialogue.moderately_damaged: Don't tell me you thought you'd won with just this~? Attacking all out even at your own expense...Fufu...Ufufufu..
dialogue.sunk: I was killed in such a flashy way~ Oh? I can see Tenryuu-chan fighting... That's good~
dialogue.rainy_season_2015: Oh, I wonder how much longer this rain will last. If it gets this humid, my wounds will ache.
dialogue.early_summer_2015: This year has become hot, hasn't it? To desire having an air conditioner in the office? I wonder what are you joking about? Those clothes of yours... I'll make them cooler for you, yeah?
dialogue.end_of_year_2015: It's the end of year, what are you doing tonight, Admiral? Hitting the bell with a certain someone? Or maybe... With me? Hehehe.
dialogue.new_year_2016: Admiral, it's a new year. This year is beginning. Happy New Year! Me and Tenryuu-chan will be in your care this year too.
dialogue.setsubun_2016: Girls~ When throwing the beans, say "Devil's out, Luck in"~ Come back to me if you're out of beans to throw, okay~? Be sure to aim well at the demon~ Hehehe~
